I was soooo impressed by the quality of the food! It was cooked perfectly! It wasn't greasy like I've experienced before with similar food. It had good flavor, and fresh garnish. If I lived in the area I would go hear all the time!! Highly recommend.

I’m curious as to who runs this restaurant and why they thought it was okay to NOT train their staff. When I walked in the door one of the servers was on their phone, I was not greeted with a hello or anything. However, I usually look past these things and am not one to complain unless the service drops downhill from there! I ordered their meal which came with two options and I ordered my pernil with white rice and lentijas. When my plate came out my pernil was hard as ROCKS and then my white rice came out as yellow rice... because they didn’t have any more white rice left over... in a Hispanic restaurant where rice is the number one thing people usually get their MEAT with, why did they run so low? also when I asked where my lentijas were, one of the servers informed me that they never had it in the first place. So to my confusion why would the other waitress let me order it? Do these people not know their own menu? why are they working here? Honestly if the staff was more helpful, welcoming and knew how to do their job the hard, the over cooked food and wait time would have been no problem! I wouldn’t ever let anyone I know go here! And honestly I wouldn’t even consider coming back here if this was the only thing opened.

Definitely will return to try other dishes.

Oh man, came here before going to a local bowling spot and I am STUFFED. The portions are more than generous and the food itself is fresh and deliciously packed with flavor. If you're a lover of traditional Dominican or Spanish cuisine in general, this is a great place to go. There are a few booths in the front and larger tables in the back, so whether you're going on a date or hanging with a group, there's perfect seating. And if you want to come alone there's 3 big flat screen TV's, a bar, and wonderful music over the speakers, so you're sure to be entertained.
